{"vv74:0.1":"Vimanavatthu ","vv74:0.2":"Purisavimana ","vv74:0.3":"Payasivagga ","vv74:0.4":"10. (Uttara) Payasivimanavatthu ","vv74:1.1":"“Ya devarajassa sabha sudhamma, ","vv74:1.2":"Yatthacchati devasangho samaggo; ","vv74:1.3":"Tathupamam tuyhamidam vimanam, ","vv74:1.4":"Obhasayam titthati antalikkhe. ","vv74:2.1":"Deviddhipattosi mahanubhavo, ","vv74:2.2":"Manussabhuto kimakasi punnam; ","vv74:2.3":"Kenasi evam jalitanubhavo, ","vv74:2.4":"Vanno ca te sabbadisa pabhasati”ti. ","vv74:3.1":"So devaputto attamano, ","vv74:3.2":"…pe… ","vv74:3.3":"yassa kammassidam phalam. ","vv74:4.1":"“Aham manussesu manussabhuto, ","vv74:4.2":"Ranno payasissa ahosim manavo; ","vv74:4.3":"Laddha dhanam samvibhagam akasim, ","vv74:4.4":"Piya ca me silavanto ahesum; ","vv74:4.5":"Annanca pananca pasannacitto, ","vv74:4.6":"Sakkacca danam vipulam adasim. ","vv74:5.1":"Tena metadiso vanno, ","vv74:5.2":"…pe… ","vv74:5.3":"Vanno ca me sabbadisa pabhasati”ti. ","vv74:6.1":"Payasivimanam dasamam. ","vv74:7.1":"Payasivaggo chattho. ","vv74:8.1":"Tassuddanam ","vv74:9.1":"Dve agarino phaladayi, ","vv74:9.2":"Dve upassayadayi bhikkhaya dayi; ","vv74:9.3":"Yavapalako ceva dve, ","vv74:9.4":"Kundalino payasiti. ","vv74:10.1":"Purisanam dutiyo vaggo pavuccatiti. "}